news_header: Ukraine rejects agreements made without its involvement; Trump aims to negotiate without being a mere messenger.
news_original_title: Analyysi: Ukrainan ympärillä tapahtuu paljon, mutta maa ei usko sen tuovan rauhaa
news_text: Ukraine is not accepting agreements made without its participation, emphasizing that negotiations are invalid without its involvement. President Zelensky expresses concern over US-Russia talks sidelining Ukraine, fearing an unfavorable peace deal. Trump aims to negotiate with Russia while prioritizing his interests.
